## Install in other projects

Copy this file to each repo:

```bash
mkdir -p .cursor/rules
cp /path/to/checkyourbackup-website/.cursor/rules/hola-adios-global.mdc .cursor/rules/
# Optional project-specific overlay:
cp /path/to/checkyourbackup-website/.cursor/rules/hola-adios-project.mdc .cursor/rules/
git add .cursor/rules/ && git commit -m "Add hola/adios session workflow rules"
```

Create `PROJECT_STATUS.md` and `TODO.md` in each project on first **adios**.

